&lt;h1&gt;Transfer Team&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking motivated and hardworking individuals to work as part of the Transfer Team for the Trust. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role will include preparing and packing patients for transfer, communicating with other staff members and transferring patients from clinical area to other clinical areas in beds and wheelchairs.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role requires a lot of patient interaction and physical exercise as you will be transferring patients in beds or chairs across the hospital throughout the shift. &lt;strong&gt;You should be a team player with excellent communication skills, as you will work closely with clinical and management teams across the organisation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date 20th November 2020&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
